>\n驕生慣養的香港人要竄入布滿曱甴、老鼠的地下水渠，爬行 1 小時逃走，為的是躲避警察的毆打，大家想想這仇恨是多麼的恐怖。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />這是林鄭月娥一手造成的，所以她的違法行為，簡單來說，她就是&quot;香港屠夫&quot;，在歷史上要留名，會被釘在十字架上。</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sd75tXk0sFY?t=321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsd75tXk0sFY%3Ft%3D321&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=6529542d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sd75tXk0sFY?t=321</a>"},{"pid":"6be834a62a084cbe6638e774d1f76f286fa38ce3","tid":2494190,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ef782910e385434293f9fa225632714d8e68f2f","tid":2494190,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aed42acb75281c0c6c1be43a7ba5d0acf3d30c9","tid":2494190,"uid":54966,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"Diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"Diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b58e8103fccd372de149652e5348de726a787d3","tid":2494190,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ef782910e385434293f9fa225632714d8e68f2f","tid":2494190,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aed42acb75281c0c6c1be43a7ba5d0acf3d30c9","tid":2494190,"uid":54966,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"Diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"Diu<img src=\"/assets/faces